OL,3,CMan who 'kicked puppy like a football'
OL,4,Cbanned from keeping animals
OL,6,FPaul Chadwick, 32, from Fazakerley,
OL,7,Fwas sentenced at Magistrates' Court on
OL,8,FTuesday 6 February after pleading
OL,9,Fguilty to an animal welfare offence at
OL,10,Fan earlier hearing.JThe court heard
OL,11,Fthat two members of the public
OL,12,Fwitnessed Chadwick kick the dog - a
OL,13,Ffive-month-old Cane Corso named Rocky
OL,14,F- at the side of Huyton Lane on 31
OL,15,FMarch 2023.JA passing police car
OL,16,Fstopped, seized Rocky from Chadwick
OL,17,Fand took him to a vets for an
OL,18,Fexamination. The police also contacted
OL,19,Fthe .
