OL,4,Cbanned from keeping animals
OL,6,FAs well as a five-year ban from owning
OL,7,Fany animals, the 32-year-old was
OL,8,Fhanded a 12-week prison sentence
OL,9,Fsuspended for 12 months, ordered to
OL,10,Fpay a #154 victim surcharge, and
OL,11,Fhanded a six-month drug rehabilitation
OL,12,Fand mental health requirement order.
OL,14,FAn expert vet witness said in a
OL,15,Fstatement in court, that members of
OL,16,Fthe public reported Chadwick to be
OL,17,F"intoxicated" as he was staggering in
OL,18,Fthe road.
