OL,3,CMan who 'kicked puppy like a football'
OL,4,Cbanned from keeping animals
OL,6,FThe statement said: "The man was seen
OL,7,Fby both witnesses to yank the dog's
OL,8,Flead multiple times and then a
OL,9,F'violent' and 'forceful' kick was made
OL,10,Fwhich appeared to connect with the
OL,11,Fdog's head.
OL,13,F"After this blow the dog was unwilling
OL,14,Fto go with the man and appeared
OL,15,Freluctant to walk with a crouched body
OL,16,Fposture."
OL,18,FThe court heard that the police
OL,19,Fofficers described the dog as
OL,20,Fappearing scared of Chadwick and
OL,21,Fcowering away from him.
