OL,4,Cbanned from keeping animals
OL,6,FThe vet said in a statement: "The dog
OL,7,Fwould have not only been suffering
OL,8,Fpain from the blows but also
OL,9,Fpsychological distress with fear from
OL,10,Fbeing injured again.J"Any owner who is
OL,11,Fcapable of striking their dog to this
OL,12,Fextent while out in a public space is
OL,13,Falso very capable of doing so in the
OL,14,Fhome environment and it is a concern
OL,15,Fthat this may not have been the first
OL,16,Ftime the dog was injured. This is
OL,17,Funacceptable."
