OL,6,FRSPCA inspector Anthony Joynes, who
OL,7,Finvestigated the incident, said after
OL,8,Fthe sentencing: "The people who
OL,9,Fwitnessed this incident said Chadwick
OL,10,Fkicked Rocky like he was a football.
OL,12,F"Thankfully Rocky made a full recovery
OL,13,Ffrom his injuries. It is wholly
OL,14,Funacceptable to treat an animal like
OL,15,Fthis.
